title: PSP Mind Challenge Package
description:
Archer Maclean&#039;s Mercury
Carol Vorderman&#039;s Sudoku
Chessmaster: The Art Of Learning
Crush
Cube: 3d Puzzle Mayhem
Frantix
Go Sudoku
Hotbrain
Mercury Meltdown
Mind Quiz
PQ2
Puzzle Quest: Challange of The Warlords
Spelling Challenges And More

Put the games in a folder named "ISO", right beside your "PSP" folder in the root of your memory stick.
I have tested all the games with 3.71, 3.80, 3.90 m33 firmware (m33 driver).
I&#039;ve included an ISO compressor in case you want to change the format of any of the games, but I think they all work fine as .cso.

I don&#039;t know how appreciated this one will be, but I love this kind of games so I figure I share them.
I know some of the games can be found elsewhere, but I hope you like the easiness of getting it all in one package.
So for those of you who like to challange your minds, enjoy! :)
